scripts by issuing the command REXX followed by your Object Rexx script
at the command prompt. To interactively try Object Rexx statements,
enter <computeroutput>rexx rexxtry.rex</computeroutput>on the command line.
Enter <computeroutput>exit</computeroutput> to end the program.
</para>
